<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/miatta-fahnbulleh> a schema1:Person ;
    dcterms:isPartOf <https://www.gov.uk/government> ;
    schema1:description "Miatta Fahnbulleh was Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State at the Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Government from 6 September 2025 to 12 May 2026. She was previously Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State at the Department for Energy Security and Net Zero between 9 July 2024 and 6 September 2025."@en ;
